OL,3,CFormer ketamine user who had bladder
OL,4,Cremoved says drug ruined his life
OL,6,FWarning: This article discusses drug-
OL,7,Fuse
OL,9,FA 25-year-old man who had to undergo
OL,10,Fbladder surgery has said that the long-
OL,11,Fterm side effects of using ketamine
OL,12,Fhave "ruined" his life.
OL,14,FOllie Westall had to undergo an
OL,15,Foperation to get a stoma bag in order
OL,16,Fto get rid of the daily pain.
