OL,3,CFormer ketamine user who had bladder
OL,4,Cremoved says drug ruined his life
OL,6,F"I actually know people who've used
OL,7,Fheroin for 30 years and they have a
OL,8,Fbetter standard of living than me," he
OL,9,Fsaid before having the surgery. "They
OL,10,Fcan do things I can't."
OL,12,FKetamine is one of the fastest growing
OL,13,Fdrugs amongst young people.
OL,15,FAccording to UK Government figures,
OL,16,Fits use has more than doubled over the
OL,17,Flast decade among young people, and
OL,18,Fresearch by University College London
OL,19,Fshows that 60% of regular ketamine
OL,20,Fusers report having bladder or nasal
OL,21,Fproblems.
