OL,3,CFormer ketamine user who had bladder
OL,4,Cremoved says drug ruined his life
OL,6,FIn a new series on S4C, Wales on
OL,7,FDrugs, Ollie said that taking the drug
OL,8,Fwas as normal as brushing his teeth
OL,9,Fwhen he was addicted to ketamine for a
OL,10,Fperiod of eight years.
OL,12,FHe said that he was only using small
OL,13,Famounts at the weekend to begin with
OL,14,Fbut this grew enormously over time and
OL,15,Fturned into a huge problem.
OL,17,FHe said: "When I was like three years
OL,18,Finto the addiction, I was using ket
OL,19,Fevery day. I was using 21 grams, and
OL,20,Fit just turned into the most normal
OL,21,Fthing."
