OL,3,CFormer ketamine user who had bladder
OL,4,Cremoved says drug ruined his life
OL,6,FBecause of the drug, Ollie began to
OL,7,Fsuffer with what he calls "ket cramps".
OL,9,FIt "felt like someone was grabbing my
OL,10,Fkidneys," he said, and "in the end,
OL,11,Fthe only thing that helped the pain...
OL,12,Fwas the ket itself".
OL,14,FHe described that period of time as a
OL,15,F"vicious cycle" of suffering the side
OL,16,Feffects of the drug and taking more of
OL,17,Fit to deal with the severe pain. As
OL,18,Fthe ketamine destroyed his bladder he
OL,19,Fbegan to pass blood and pieces of the
OL,20,Flining of the organ as well.
