OL,6,FThe ketamine also affected the size of
OL,7,Fhis bladder, drastically reducing the
OL,8,Famount he could hold and causing him
OL,9,Fto need to pass water "every sixty
OL,10,Fseconds".
OL,12,FSpeaking before having the surgery to
OL,13,Fremove his bladder, Ollie said he
OL,14,Fwould go through multiple packets of
OL,15,Fincontinence pads in a week.
OL,17,FHe said: "I've been wearing
OL,18,Fincontinence pads since I was 20... I
OL,19,Fgo through two packets a week because
OL,20,Fof the damage it's done," he said.
