OL,3,CFormer ketamine user who had bladder
OL,4,Cremoved says drug ruined his life
OL,6,F"I have to change my bedclothes every
OL,7,Fday and I wake up every night soaking
OL,8,Fwet. I wasn't aware of these effects
OL,9,Fwhen I started taking ket."
OL,11,FNow recovered from his surgery, Ollie
OL,12,Fis campaigning to improve awareness of
OL,13,Fthe effects of the drug and the
OL,14,Fsupport available to people who are
OL,15,Faddicted to it.
OL,17,FHe is determined to use his experience
OL,18,Fto help others and has set up
OL,19,F'Ketamine Support Wales' - a weekly
OL,20,Fgroup that offers support to people
OL,21,Fexperiencing problems with the drug.
